I dont understand why its necessery to log in with my full details every time.
column17: Logging in needs to be a lot faster and smoother. Eg: the pinpad shows up before its clickable, resulting in incorrect pin entered if youre trying to be fast. Also the fact that theres no animation feedback when you click a pinpad button is disruptive, and you cant trll if you pressed the button unless youre looking at the 4 dots. Instead, the button should clearly animate (invert black and white, glow effect, enlarge, whatever) so theres better feedback.
